# BCC Cr (G-type antiferromagnet) — non-collinear magmom test fixture.
# Trailing 5–7 columns are mx my mz (μB). Cr's nearest-neighbor moments
# point antiparallel; here we tilt them slightly off-z to exercise the
# vector path (not pure collinear).
CRYSTAL
PRIMVEC
   2.910000   0.000000   0.000000
   0.000000   2.910000   0.000000
   0.000000   0.000000   2.910000
PRIMCOORD
2 1
Cr   0.000000   0.000000   0.000000    0.30   0.10    1.95
Cr   1.455000   1.455000   1.455000   -0.30  -0.10   -1.95
